### 创建一个新作业
POST http://localhost:8080/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "阅读《三国演义》第1回并完成练习题",
  "bookTitle": "三国演义",
  "chapter": "第1回 宴桃园豪杰三结义",
  "dueDate": "2026-03-10"
}

### 给作业 1 新增一道题
POST http://localhost:8080/assignments/1/questions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "MCQ",
  "text": "这一章中，孙悟空最后成了什么角色？",
  "options": [
    "A. 天兵",
    "B. 猴王",
    "C. 龙王",
    "D. 神仙"
  ],
  "correctAnswer": "B"
}

### 学生提交作业 1 的答案
POST http://localhost:8080/assignments/1/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "answers": [
    { "questionId": 1, "answer": "A" },
    { "questionId": 2, "answer": "这章主要讲的是石猴出生并成为猴王的过程" },
    { "questionId": 5, "answer": "B" }
  ]
}

### 1. 不带分页参数，直接查全部作业
GET http://localhost:8080/assignments
{
  "content": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "...",
      "bookTitle": "西游记",
      "chapter": "...",
      "dueDate": "2026-03-01"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "...",
      "bookTitle": "哈利·波特与魔法石",
      "chapter": "...",
      "dueDate": "2026-03-05"
    }
  ],
  "totalElements": 2,
  "totalPages": 1,
  "number": 0,
  "size": 10
}
### 2. 每页 1 条，第一页（page 从 0 开始）
GET http://localhost:8080/assignments?page=0&size=1

### 3. 每页 1 条，第二页
GET http://localhost:8080/assignments?page=1&size=1

### 4. 按书名模糊筛选（比如只看“西游”）
GET http://localhost:8080/assignments?bookTitle=西游

### A1. 老师创建一个新作业（三国演义）
POST http://localhost:8080/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "阅读《三国演义》第1回并完成练习题",
  "bookTitle": "三国演义",
  "chapter": "第1回 宴桃园豪杰三结义",
  "dueDate": "2026-03-10"
}

### A2. 查询全部作业，确认新作业出现了
GET http://localhost:8080/assignments

### A3. 修改作业 6
PUT http://localhost:8080/assignments/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "【修改后】阅读《三国演义》第1回并完成练习题",
  "bookTitle": "三国演义",
  "chapter": "第1回 宴桃园豪杰三结义",
  "dueDate": "2026-03-15"
}

### D1. 删除多余的三国演义作业（举例）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/assignments/3

### 把作业 1 的第 1 题分值改成 2 分
PUT http://localhost:8080/questions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignmentId": 1,
  "type": "MCQ",
  "text": "孙悟空是从哪里出生的？",
  "options": [
    "A. 花果山的一块石头",
    "B. 东海龙宫",
    "C. 天庭",
    "D. 西天极乐世界"
  ],
  "correctAnswer": "A",
  "score": 2,
  "difficulty": "EASY"
}

### 把作业 1 的第 2 题分值改成 3 分
PUT http://localhost:8080/questions/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignmentId": 1,
  "type": "SHORT",
  "text": "用一句话概括这一章的主要内容。",
  "options": [],
  "correctAnswer": "这章主要讲的是石猴出生并成为猴王的过程",
  "score": 3,
  "difficulty": "MEDIUM"
}

### 学生提交作业 1 的答案（全对）
POST http://localhost:8080/assignments/1/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "answers": [
    { "questionId": 1, "answer": "A" },
    { "questionId": 2, "answer": "这章主要讲的是石猴出生并成为猴王的过程" }
  ]
}

### 老师：查看作业1有哪些提交
GET http://localhost:8080/teacher/assignments/1/submissions

### 老师：查看 submissionId=1 的每题详情
GET http://localhost:8080/teacher/submissions/1

### 家长：查看 test-student 的提交记录
GET http://localhost:8080/parent/students/test-student/submissions

### 家长：查看 submission 1 的详情
GET http://localhost:8080/parent/submissions/1
